  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed research is to examine the effect of injecting a large volume of HA (10cc) at
      the time of post arthroscopy suture removal (9-11 day post surgery), in patients with
      cartilage damage of ICRS grade 2 and above in one of the knee compartments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
