  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult Men and Women, who underwent arthroscopy of the knee with cartilage injury of
             ICRS grade 2 or higher in one of the compartments (in addition to other injuries such
             as meniscal tear and cruciate ligament).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with known rheumatic disorders.

          -  Known hypersensitivity to HA.

          -  Synovial diseases like PVNS, under 18y old.
      </textblock>
